{{/* User-prompt template for the extraction step. The system prompt
   (chatExtractionSystemPrompt in chat/extract.go) sets the schema and
   rules; this template provides the inputs.

   Variables:
     .Questions — []QuestionView{ID, Prompt}
     .Messages  — []TranscriptLine{Role, Content}
*/ -}}

# Questions on file

{{range .Questions -}}
({{.ID}}) {{.Prompt}}
{{end}}

# Transcript (verbatim)

{{range .Messages -}}
[{{.Role}}] {{.Content}}

{{end}}

Now emit the JSON object exactly per the schema in the system prompt.
Omit `answers` keys for any question the user did not substantively
answer. Use the user's voice, never the assistant's.
